OL,3,CWoman who had three miscarriages calls
OL,4,Cfor baby loss certificates in Wales
OL,6,FA woman who suffered three
OL,7,Fmiscarriages says parents in Wales who
OL,8,Fhave experienced baby loss should be
OL,9,Fable to apply for a certificate to
OL,10,Frecognise their child's life.
OL,12,FEleanor London suffered two
OL,13,Fmiscarriages while living in England,
OL,14,Fand one while living in Wales.
OL,16,FIn England, those who have lost a baby
OL,17,Fbefore 24 weeks of pregnancy are able
OL,18,Fto apply for baby loss certificates,
OL,19,Fbut there is currently no similar
OL,20,Fscheme in Wales.
