OL,3,CWoman who had three miscarriages calls
OL,4,Cfor baby loss certificates in Wales
OL,6,FEleanor says she was left "devastated"
OL,7,Fafter being told she was not eligible
OL,8,Ffor the UK Government's baby loss
OL,9,Fcertificate scheme because she has a
OL,10,FWelsh address.
OL,12,FAfter applying, Eleanor soon realised
OL,13,Fshe could not continue with the
OL,14,Fapplication using her Welsh address,
OL,15,Fdespite experiencing two of the losses
OL,16,Fin England.
OL,18,F"I felt utterly disappointed and
OL,19,Fdevastated by the whole thing," she
OL,20,Ftold ITV Cymru Wales. "I can't do
OL,21,Fanything about it."
