OL,6,F"Within the last 20-30 years, there
OL,7,Fwill be thousands of women in Wales in
OL,8,Fthe same position as me.
OL,10,F"It matters because you won't ever
OL,11,Fforget a pregnancy. It's still a part
OL,12,Fof me, it's a part of my life, it's a
OL,13,Fpart of my family's life and it's a
OL,14,Fpart of my history."
