OL,3,CWoman who had three miscarriages calls
OL,4,Cfor baby loss certificates in Wales
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government declined ITV
OL,7,FWales' request for an interview, and
OL,8,Fsaid in a statement: "The loss of a
OL,9,Fbaby at any stage of pregnancy is
OL,10,Fdevastating. We are committed to
OL,11,Fensuring every family is properly
OL,12,Fsupported during this time.
OL,14,F"All families who experience pregnancy
OL,15,Floss at maternity units in Wales are
OL,16,Fsupported by bereavement midwives, in
OL,17,Fconjunction with the charity Sands,
OL,18,Fand offered memory boxes, which
OL,19,Finclude a certificate of birth.
