OL,6,F"We are working with the UK Government
OL,7,Fto extend baby loss certificates to
OL,8,FWales. We are also working with Sands
OL,9,Fto develop a national bereavement care
OL,10,Fpathway for miscarriage, stillbirth
OL,11,Fand baby loss."
OL,13,FMorgan's Wings, a Cardiff-based
OL,14,Fcharity which supports parents through
OL,15,Fmiscarriage, offer "certificates of
OL,16,Flife" for parents who have experienced
OL,17,Fa miscarriage before 24 weeks.
